  "description": "A plant-based tray bake that's packed with delectable veg, and jives well with meat-free bacon and chive. You'll roast potato, pepper and tomato, before topping with vegan lardons and tangy dressing. All Health Hub recipes meet one of these criteria: <600 calories, 3 of your 5/day, or a source of protein.\n",
